# Wavelength — Landing Page

**Level 1 · Task 2 — Landing Page Project**

A single-page, responsive landing page for *Wavelength*, a fictional real-time API monitoring product for engineering teams. Built with plain HTML and CSS (plus a small vanilla JS snippet for the animated hero graphic) to demonstrate layout, sectioning, spacing, and color-system fundamentals.

## Live preview

Open `landing-page.html` directly in any browser — no build step, no server, no dependencies to install.

## What's inside

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `landing-page.html` | The full project — HTML, CSS, and JS in one file |
